results.title: Live Laugh Love Sterling Silver Charm-Siam Swarovski Crystals-Red Crystal and Sterling Chain Necklace-Heart Necklace-Valentine’s Day Gift
results.description:
A charm necklace is the perfect gift for that special someone! It can be a reflection of their interests, loves, adventures, feelings, and so much more.I create my necklaces using three 6mm Swarovski Crystals in various color combinations. I sometimes add beautiful Swarovski pearls for a soft shimmer. These crystals are separated with sterling silver flower spacers and 3mm round sterling beads. The colors that I choose reflect the nature of the charm. The chain is a 22 inch sterling silver cable chain with a lobster claw clasp made in Italy.
     This necklace is perfect for someone who likes the expression Live Laugh Love! Written on both sides, the heart is a little less than an inch wide and the crystal pendant is an inch and a half long. Light Siam is a beautiful shade of red and one of my favorites; perfect for Valentine’s Day. Your necklace arrives in a white satin pouch and a gift card is available on request.

results.title: Prophetic Words/Acronym Charm - BEBIS HOPE - Live Love Laugh
results.description:
When I purchased this charm, I had no idea how God was going to whisper these as acronyms. But then one day he whispered-
I LIVE because he chose me as it says in Psalm 139. I LOVE because he first loved me as it says in 1 John 4:19. I then read the proverbs 31 woman and understood why I can LAUGH. I love how he whispers to me. Be still enough to hear his whispers and embrace the ability to Live, Love & Laugh. 

Your purchasing inspirational/uplifting/motivational words on matte card stock with a charm and lobster clasp to add to any existing bracelet you may have. There is artwork available at BebisHope.com

Zinc Alloy-Lead & Nickel Free

Matte Card stock

The acronyms are words that have been whispered over the last 32 years to inspire and encourage one another with HOPE. Behind every acronym there is a story. Its amazing how each one has touched someones life. Create your own story and put these charms on a key chain or existing bracelet so you can share your story of HOPE! To date there have been over 80 acronyms whispered and my goal is to put them either in book form or app form to be shared. After all ... all I want to do is PLANT-Pray Love And Nurture Truth.

Thank you for taking time to read about us and share BEBIS HOPE!
